OL,3,CMan who killed grandmother to gain
OL,4,Cmoney from will jailed for 26 years
OL,6,FA man who snuck into his grandmother's
OL,7,Fhouse while she slept and strangled
OL,8,Fher to gain money from her will, has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for life with a minimum
OL,10,Fterm of 26 years, as his mother
OL,11,Fdeclared she will struggle to forgive
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,FJoshua Powell, 27, killed 96-year-old
OL,15,FEmma Finch and then set fire to her
OL,16,Fhome in Mill Road, Liss, Hampshire, in
OL,17,Fthe early hours of May 17 last year.
