OL,6,F"You repaid her kindness by savagely
OL,7,Fkilling her in the expectation of
OL,8,Fgaining money from her death under her
OL,9,Fwill.
OL,11,F"It is clear you intended to kill Emma
OL,12,FFinch, your grandmother. You then
OL,13,Ftried to cover your tracks by setting
OL,14,Fa fire, intending to destroy Emma
OL,15,FFinch's body, and telling lies."
