OL,6,FMs Finch had two children, six
OL,7,Fgrandchildren and three great-
OL,8,Fgrandchildren, and some of them said,
OL,9,Fin victim impact statements read out
OL,10,Fby the prosecutor, that they will
OL,11,Fnever forgive Powell.
OL,13,FThe defendant's mother, Catherine
OL,14,FPowell, who is Ms Finch's daughter,
OL,15,Fsaid she "will struggle ever to
OL,16,Fforgive him for what he has done".
OL,26,@wD@JOUxD@aO]
