OL,6,FPeter Finch, Ms Finch's son and
OL,7,FPowell's uncle, said: "One of my
OL,8,Fbiggest fears is that mum in those
OL,9,Ffinal seconds before she lost
OL,10,Fconsciousness as you were strangling
OL,11,Fher, that she knew it was you Joshua
OL,12,Fand that being her final, haunting
OL,13,Fmemory that she took to her grave.
OL,15,F"You, Joshua, betrayed your mum's,
OL,16,Fyour oma's, love that night and that
OL,17,Fis something for which I can never
OL,18,Fforgive you.
OL,20,F"I hope you are deeply tormented by
OL,21,Fthose acts for the rest of your life.
