OL,6,F"Did my mum, your oma, really deserve
OL,7,Fto be murdered for the balance of your
OL,8,Finheritance? The question that only
OL,9,Fyou can answer."
OL,11,FAfter the sentencing, the family said
OL,12,Fin a statement: "There are no words
OL,13,Fthat can soften the pain we as a
OL,14,Ffamily have endured over the last 18
OL,15,Fmonths since those tragic events on
OL,16,Fthe 17th of May 2024, but today's
OL,17,Fconviction will finally help to ease
OL,18,Fthat pain as we finally come to terms
OL,19,Fwith mum's untimely death.
