OL,4,Cmoney from will jailed for 26 years
OL,6,F"Mum throughout her amazing long life
OL,7,Fshowed great courage and perseverance,
OL,8,Fwe as a family must now do the same as
OL,9,Fwe begin the process to rebuild our
OL,10,Fshattered lives with her ever in our
OL,11,Fthoughts and prayers.
OL,13,F"Mum can now finally rest in peace
OL,14,Fknowing that justice has been served
OL,15,Fand her grandson will now spend a
OL,16,Fsignificant period of his life
OL,17,Fincarcerated for her murder."
OL,19,FIn his letter to the court, Powell
OL,20,Fsaid he does not forgive himself.
