OL,6,F"Forgiveness is not something I expect
OL,7,Ffrom any member of the family. Not
OL,8,Feven I forgive the actions I took on
OL,9,Fthat fateful day.
OL,11,F"The guilt is something I will have to
OL,12,Flearn to live with. It eats away at
OL,13,Fme, gnawing my bran and thoughts every
OL,14,Fsingle second each day.
OL,16,F"From the bottom of my now destroyed
OL,17,Fheart and soul I truly am sorry."
