OL,6,FBefore the attack, CCTV showed Powell,
OL,7,Fwho worked as a cashier at Tesco,
OL,8,Fleaving his flat with a belt which he
OL,9,Flater discarded in bushes.
OL,11,FThe fire service was alerted at about
OL,12,F4am by an automatic alarm triggered by
OL,13,Fthe activation of a carbon monoxide
OL,14,Fmonitor at Ms Finch's home.
OL,16,FFirefighters had to force entry to the
OL,17,Fhouse, where Ms Finch was found dead,
OL,18,Fbut discovered that a key safe outside
OL,19,Fthe back door was open and the key was
OL,20,Fmissing.
