OL,6,FThe combination to the safe was later
OL,7,Ffound in a note on Powell's phone.
OL,9,FHe had, at the time of the incident,
OL,10,Fswitched off the location finder on
OL,11,Fhis phone, but police were able to
OL,12,Ftrack his movements in his car.
OL,14,FThe court heard Powell owed his
OL,15,Flandlord #2,500 and was also in about
OL,16,F#8,000 of debt to various other
OL,17,Fcompanies.
