OL,6,FWeeks before Ms Finch's death, he is
OL,7,Fsaid to have told friends he "hoped
OL,8,Fthat his nan died soon because he was
OL,9,Fskint and that he thought he was the
OL,10,Fonly one getting money in the will
OL,11,Fwhen she died".
OL,13,FOn the day of her death, he spoke to a
OL,14,Fwork colleague about the prospect of
OL,15,Finheritance and how much he understood
OL,16,Fhis grandmother's estate to be worth.
