OL,6,FThe court heard that Powell was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with Tourette syndrome and
OL,8,Ffound to have reduced cognitive
OL,9,Ffunction, but the judge said he "knew
OL,10,Fperfectly well the difference between
OL,11,Fright and wrong".
OL,13,FPowell, of Elmfield Court, Lindford,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty in May to murdering his
OL,15,Fgrandmother.
